<lyrics>[V1]
 (kyf tskt ʿn sẖʿbk .. whw yrqd fy ạltrạb)2
 wʿdk ạ̉n tkẖrj yạ rḥym .. brh mtẖl ạlḍyạʾ
 (hạ ạ̉nạ fy ạltẖgẖr wạqf .. rạfʿ qlby lk)2
 bạlạ̹ymạn qlby mbṣr .. sẖʿby mlkaⁿạ lk
 (yạ ạ̹lh ạlḥb wạlslṭạn .. fltgẖr ʿly̱ ạsmk)2
 lạ ykn fy wsṭ sẖʿbk .. (mdẖbḥaⁿạ lgẖyrk)2</lyrics>
